init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.
text:
All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.
Dads all over the world were shocked. How did it happen? Some blame the economy, others say it's because of a gender bias. Some even blamed voodoo witch doctors, where ever the finger could be pointed.

Some dad mugs still said #1 though. Scientist started looking into the reason behind it. 
The reason the Dad mugs no longer said #1 was found out, kind of. At least the reasons behind it was clear even if no one understood how it happened. 

You see, what they found out was that the mugs really started to show how good of a dad a man was to his kids. The mugs were a window into the dad's soul. If he did not care about his children, then his mug would give a really low rating like #384657, or something like that.
If a dad really cared about his children a lot then the mug would say a really high number like dad #3 or 9 or even 7. 

Now, there were some dads who did have a #1 mug, but those mugs where really only for the best of the best dads in the world. The one who did anything for their child. Taught them, guided them, never missed a softball game, and even took the team out for pizza after the game. 

The #1 Dad Mug was for the dad who would never let his kids down. The dad who really, and truly loved and would gladly sacrifice for his kids. Some dads got jealous, but to a good effect because they tried harder to be good dads, and not just fathers.

text: In every country, every city, and on every street corner there was an ugly fight between men holding "#1 Dad" mugs.
How did Dad lose to these people?
Some blame the economy, others say it's because of a gender bias.
The results were in from the DNA test.
Why is it that Moms are in the top spot?

info.name: suggestion-open
text: You see, there was a big secret behind the mugs that show "#1 Dad."
They deduced that the #1 ranking would always stay in the brain of a human Dad, even if on the outside it showed something else.
Answers were not easy to find.
They ran tests and couldn't find anything different.
The reason the Dad mugs no longer said #1 was found out.

info.name: suggestion-open
text: What was in the dad mugs was some kind of magical material that detected some sort of "dadness" in a man.
There was a formula to it.
The mugs were a window into the dad's soul.
The amount of quality time a dad had with his kids.
And they only showed this if the Dads did their best to be there for their kids.

info.name: suggestion-open
text: I guess that made sense.
Now, there were some dads who did not have a #1 mug.
When the mugs were displayed they all looked equal.
This was a phenomenon that could not be explained, so all the dad mugs were taken away and replaced with new ones.
It varied depending on how caring the dad was towards his kids.

info.name: suggestion-open
text: A dad like that would be a #1 Dad to his children.
It was a very select group of dads.
The #1 Dad Mug was for the dad who would never let his kids down.
He was the best of dads.
Women also got in on the act too.
